[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">assembled</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> was <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him. He <st data-num=\"07760 05921\">appointed</st> <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of <st data-num=\"0505\" class=\"\">thousands</st> and <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">hundreds</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> then <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent out</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>\u2014a <st data-num=\"07992\" class=\"\">third</st> under the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">leadership</st> of <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st>, a <st data-num=\"07992\" class=\"\">third</st> under the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">leadership</st> of <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brother</st> <st data-num=\"052\" class=\"\">Abishai</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"06870\" class=\"\">Zeruiah</st>, and a <st data-num=\"07992\" class=\"\">third</st> under the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">leadership</st> of <st data-num=\"0863\" class=\"\">Ittai</st> the <st data-num=\"01663\" class=\"\">Gittite</st>. The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">troops</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">too</st> will <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">indeed</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">march out</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">But the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cYou should <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">do this</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> we should have to <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">make a rapid</st> <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">retreat</st>, they <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">won\u2019t</st> be <st data-num=\"07760 03820\">concerned</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">about</st> us.<n id=\"3\" /> Even <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st> of us should <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">die</st>, they <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">won\u2019t</st> be <st data-num=\"07760 03820\">concerned</st>. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st><n id=\"4\" /> are <st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">like</st> <st data-num=\"06235 0505\" class=\"\">10,000</st> of us! <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">So</st> it is <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">better</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">if</st> you <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">remain</st> in the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> for <st data-num=\"05826\" class=\"\">support</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "Then the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> them, \u201cI will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whatever</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">seems</st> <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">best</st> to you.\u201d<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stayed</st> <st data-num=\"0413 03027\">beside</st> the city <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gate</st>, while <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">marched out</st> by <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">hundreds</st> and by <st data-num=\"0505\" class=\"\">thousands</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">gave</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">order to</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st>, <st data-num=\"052\" class=\"\">Abishai</st>, and <st data-num=\"0863\" class=\"\">Ittai:</st> \u201cFor my sake deal <st data-num=\"0328\" class=\"\">gently</st> with the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young man</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>.\u201d Now the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> was <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listening</st> when the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">gave</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st> this <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">order</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">concerning</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">marched out</st> to the <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">field</st> to <st data-num=\"07125\" class=\"\">fight against</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. The <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">took place</st> in the <st data-num=\"03293\" class=\"\">forest</st> of <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> was <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">defeated</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">men</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"04046\" class=\"\">slaughter</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"06242 0505\">20,000</st> soldiers were killed.",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"06327\" class=\"\">spread out</st> <st data-num=\"05921 06440\">over</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">area</st>, and the <st data-num=\"03293\" class=\"\">forest</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumed</st> <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">more</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">than</st> the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">devoured</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"07122\" class=\"\">happened to come</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">across</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">men</st>. Now as <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> was <st data-num=\"07392\" class=\"\">riding</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> his<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06505\" class=\"\">mule</st>, <st data-num=\"06505\" class=\"\">it</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">under</st> the <st data-num=\"07730\" class=\"\">branches</st> of a <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">large</st> <st data-num=\"0424\" class=\"\">oak tree</st>. His <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">got caught</st> in the <st data-num=\"0424\" class=\"\">oak</st> and he was <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">suspended</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">in</st> <st data-num=\"08064 0996 0776\">midair</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> while the <st data-num=\"06505\" class=\"\">mule</st> he had <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">been</st> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">riding</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">kept going</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st><n id=\"1\" /> of the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> this, he <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">reported</st> it to <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201cI <st data-num=\"02009 07200\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"08518\" class=\"\">hanging</st> in an <st data-num=\"0424\" class=\"\">oak tree</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> to the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> who was <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">telling</st> him this, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">What</st>! You <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> this? <st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">Why</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">didn\u2019t</st> you <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">strike</st> him <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">down</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">right</st> on <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">the spot</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">would</st> have <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> you <st data-num=\"06235\" class=\"\">10</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">pieces of silver</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">a</st> <st data-num=\"02290\" class=\"\">commemorative belt</st>!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03863\" class=\"\">Even if</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> were <st data-num=\"08254 05921 03709\">receiving</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0505\" class=\"\">1,000</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">pieces of silver</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> I would <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07971 03027 0413\">strike</st><n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>! In our <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">presence</st><n id=\"5\" /> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">gave</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">order</st> to you and <st data-num=\"052\" class=\"\">Abishai</st> and <st data-num=\"0863\" class=\"\">Ittai</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">Protect</st> the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young man</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> for my sake.\u2019<n id=\"6\" />",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0176\" class=\"\">If</st> I had <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">acted</st> <st data-num=\"08267\">at risk</st> of my own <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">life</st><n id=\"1\" />\u2014and <st data-num=\"03605 01697 03808\">nothing</st> is <st data-num=\"03582\" class=\"\">hidden</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> would have <st data-num=\"03320 05048\">abandoned</st> me.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cI will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03176\" class=\"\">wait around</st> <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">like this</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">for</st> you!\u201d He <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> <st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">spears</st> in his <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">hand</st> and <st data-num=\"08628\" class=\"\">thrust</st> them into the <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">middle</st> of <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> while he was <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">still</st> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">alive</st> in the <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">middle</st> of the <st data-num=\"0424\" class=\"\">oak tree</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">Then</st> <st data-num=\"06235\" class=\"\">10</st> <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> who were <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">armor</st>-<st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">bearers</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">struck</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> and <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">finished</st> him <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">off</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"08628\" class=\"\">blew</st> the <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">trumpet</st><n id=\"1\" /> and the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turned back</st> from <st data-num=\"07291 0310\">chasing</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> had <st data-num=\"02820\" class=\"\">called</st> for the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"02820\" class=\"\">to halt</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>, <st data-num=\"07993\" class=\"\">threw</st> him <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">into</st> a <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">large</st> <st data-num=\"06354\" class=\"\">pit</st> in the <st data-num=\"03293\" class=\"\">forest</st>, and <st data-num=\"05324\" class=\"\">stacked</st> a <st data-num=\"01419 03966\">huge</st> <st data-num=\"01530\" class=\"\">pile</st> of <st data-num=\"068\" class=\"\">stones</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> him. In the meantime <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">fled</st> to their <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">homes</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">Before this</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st><n id=\"2\" /> had <st data-num=\"03947 05324\">set up</st> a <st data-num=\"04678 0834\">monument</st><n id=\"3\" /> and dedicated it to himself in the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06010\" class=\"\">Valley</st>, <st data-num=\"03588 0559\">reasoning</st>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"05668\" class=\"\">who will</st> <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">carry on</st> my <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>.\u201d He <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">named</st> the <st data-num=\"04678\" class=\"\">monument</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">after</st> <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">himself</st>, and <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> it is <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">known</st> as <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">Memorial</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"0290\" class=\"\">Ahimaaz</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"06659\" class=\"\">Zadok</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">Let</st> me <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">run</st> and <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">give</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> the <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">good news</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">vindicated</st> him <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">before</st> his <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "But <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to him, \u201c<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">bearer</st> of <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">good news</st> <st data-num=\"03117 02088\">today</st>. You will <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">bear good news</st> some <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">other</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>, but <st data-num=\"03808 01319\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03117 02088\">today</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588 05921 03651\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">is dead</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st> and <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">tell</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> you have <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">seen</st>.\u201d After <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bowing</st> to <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st>, the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">ran off</st>.",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0290\" class=\"\">Ahimaaz</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"06659\" class=\"\">Zadok</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st> <st data-num=\"03254 0559\">spoke</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Whatever</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">happens</st>, <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">let</st> <st data-num=\"01571 0589\">me</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">go</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">after</st> the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st>.\u201d But <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> is <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">it</st> that <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> want to <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">go</st>, my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>? You have <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"01309\" class=\"\">good news</st> that will <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">bring</st> you a <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">reward</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "But he said,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Whatever</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">happens</st>, I want to <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">go</st>!\u201d So Joab<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to him, \u201cThen <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">go</st>!\u201d So <st data-num=\"0290\" class=\"\">Ahimaaz</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">ran</st> by the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> of the Jordan <st data-num=\"03603\" class=\"\">plain</st>, and he <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">passed</st> the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Now <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> was <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">sitting</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">between</st> the <st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">inner and outer</st> <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gates</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and the <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watchman</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> up <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01406\" class=\"\">roof</st> over the <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gate</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">wall</st>. When he <st data-num=\"05375 05869\">looked</st>, he <st data-num=\"07200 02009\">saw</st> a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">running</st> <st data-num=\"0905\" class=\"\">by</st> himself. ",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "So the <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watchman</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">called out</st> and <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">informed</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>. The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> he is <st data-num=\"0905\" class=\"\">by</st> himself, he <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">brings</st> <st data-num=\"01309\" class=\"\">good news</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> The runner<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">ever</st> <st data-num=\"07131\" class=\"\">closer</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watchman</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">another</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">running</st>. The <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watchman</st> <st data-num=\"07121 0559\">called out</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"07778\" class=\"\">gatekeeper</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">There is</st> another <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">running</st> <st data-num=\"0905\" class=\"\">by</st> himself.\u201d The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">This one</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">also</st> is <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">bringing good news</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watchman</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cIt <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">appears</st> to <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">me</st> that the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"04794\" class=\"\">runner</st> is <st data-num=\"04794 0290\">Ahimaaz</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"06659\" class=\"\">Zadok</st>.\u201d The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">He</st> is a <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>, and he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">comes</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st> <st data-num=\"01309\" class=\"\">news</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"0290\" class=\"\">Ahimaaz</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">called out</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">Greetings</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> He <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bowed down</st> before the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> with his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">face</st> toward the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cMay the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> be <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">praised</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">because</st> he has <st data-num=\"05462\" class=\"\">defeated</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> <st data-num=\"05375 03027\">opposed</st><n id=\"3\" /> my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">How</st> is the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young man</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>?\u201d <st data-num=\"0290\" class=\"\">Ahimaaz</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cI <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> a <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great deal</st> of <st data-num=\"01995\" class=\"\">confusion</st> when <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> was <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sending</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> and me, your <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>, but I <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> it was all about.\u201d",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">Turn aside</st> and <st data-num=\"03320\" class=\"\">take</st> your <st data-num=\"03320\" class=\"\">place</st> <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">here</st>.\u201d So he <st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">turned aside</st> and <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">waited</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Then</st> the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> and <st data-num=\"0559 03569\">said</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cMay my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> now <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">receive the good news</st>! The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"03588 08199\">vindicated</st> you <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> and delivered you from the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who have <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">rebelled</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> you!\u201d<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">asked</st> the <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">How</st> is the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young man</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>?\u201d The <st data-num=\"03569\" class=\"\">Cushite</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cMay the <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> of my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> have <st data-num=\"06965 07451\">plotted</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> like that <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young man</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">(19:1)<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> then <st data-num=\"07264\" class=\"\">became</st> very <st data-num=\"07264\" class=\"\">upset</st>. He <st data-num=\"05927\">went up</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05944\" class=\"\">upper room</st> over the <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gate</st> and <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">wept</st>. As he <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> he <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st>, \u201cMy <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>! My <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>! <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">If</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">only</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> could have <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">in your place</st>! <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>, my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "33"
  }
]